verbose_text: We found that treating mice with the AA98 antibody had no effect on either the number of lymphocytes or the proportions of various lymphocyte sub-populations (including CD146 + lymphocytes) within the peripheral immune system (XREF_FIG); the antibody also had no effect on IFNgamma or IL-17 expression in CD4 + T cells within the CNS lesions (XREF_FIG).
